page.title: 13Wetwang,Churches
page.content: There are two churches in Wetwang.Both of them are in the Main Street and each one has a service on a Sunday. St.Paul's Methodist Church usually has a service starting at 10.45am.and St.Nicholas'C.ofE.Church is at 9.30am. or at 6pm.depending on which week in the month it is.There is a notice board outside which will tell you. On the second Sunday in each month the two churches join together at 11o'clock for a service. There is a Sunday School at St.Paul's and a choir at St.Nicholas'. You can go to both if you want to.
